subject: Automobile Racing
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Jamie McMurray won the 2010 Daytona 500 and produced one of the most successful runs in the Sprint Cup Series last year after falling short of expectations earlier in his career.
